strings: <voice_0x010012BB><se_high>Jessica: When I ran away from home, I thought that if I could only stop Dhoulmagus, I'd at least have avenged Alistair's death.
<voice_0x010012BC><se_high>Jessica: But it turns out Dhoulmagus was just a puppet. Rhapthorne is the real villain.
<voice_0x010012BD><se_high>Jessica: You know...I can't help wondering what chance people like us stand against an enemy like that... It seems so hopeless...
<voice_0x010012BE><se_high>Jessica: Ugh, listen to me. I sound like such a wimp!

<voice_0x010012BF><se_high>Jessica: I don't know what's got into me lately.
I'm normally the one giving everyone else encouragement, right?
<voice_0x010012C0><se_high>Jessica: Hey! ...Well, I suppose you provide your fair share of encouragement too.

<voice_0x010012C1><se_high>Jessica: Do you really think so?
Ha ha! You're always so kind...

<voice_0x010012C4><se_high>Jessica: We've got an early start tomorrow.
We should probably get some sleep.
<voice_0x010012C6><se_high>Jessica: Once all this is over, I'll be back, I promise.
